Interface Modifier

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractModifier, ClientSideBigDataModifier, CoerceTypeModifier, PassThroughModifier, ServerSideBigDataModifier

    public interface Modifier
    Pluggable feature that may be used to modify the content of a message before it is serialized and sent and/or modify it after it was received and deserialized.
